message: To get 100 points, filter *one magical liquid/gas* and *one mundane liquid/gas*. Then combine these two filtered items. For example, 'filtered basilisk venom' (magical) + 'filtered honey nectar' (mundane) makes 100 points. Vial solid items to make 'extracted' liquids. Combining two 'extracted' items (mundane) or two 'filtered' items (magical) generally yields 60 points. Combining 'extracted' items with 'filtered' items often leads to lower scores of 30 or 60, so focus on the 'filtered magical' + 'filtered mundane' pair for max value.

message: Always use 'filter' on liquids/gases and 'vial' on solids first. Each tool use results in a 30 value item. To reach 60, combine two items that are ALIKE in TWO ways: 1) same process type (both 'filtered' OR both 'extracted') AND 2) same magic type (both 'magical' OR both 'mundane'). Mixing 'filtered' with 'extracted' or 'magical' with 'mundane' usually results in lower or negative values. Submitting at 60 is often optimal as further combinations rarely improve and can decrease value significantly.
